libpathrs: This library implements a set of C-friendly APIs (written in Rust) to
libpathrs: make path resolution within a potentially-untrusted directory safe on
libpathrs: GNU/Linux. [Thereare countless examples of security vulnerabilities
libpathrs: caused by bad handling of paths][avoidable-issues]; this library
libpathrs: provides an easy-to-use set of VFS APIs to avoid those kinds of
libpathrs: issues.
